{"tid":2120750,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"飄洋過海到英國G5升學 或成文社科學術科最佳出路","createTime":"2020-07-23T01:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T01:36:49.000Z","uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6542e1870fbba46543a3e00594067cabdd969a","tid":2120750,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WRBBU7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WRBBU7.png&h=f88b01fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林綽宏接受本報訪問指出，今年困難重重，應考時仍可保持水準，故很滿意自己表現。他早在初中已計劃到<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">英國劍橋大學升學</span></span>，從小喜歡研究機械運作原理，長大後自學電腦編程語言，曾參加相關比賽，故選讀工程系。<br />\n<br />\n沈旭程表示自己的理想是尋求公義，所以打算修讀<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">法律</span></span>學科，現時正<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">考慮到英國升學</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n羅穎賢在數學延伸部分M1同樣獲5**佳績，成為「超級狀元」。她表示收到喜訊時，感到難以置信，回過神後便感到興奮，喜出望外，同時也很開心自己的努力得到肯定。她表示計劃到<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">英國牛津大學修讀英語與文學</span></span>（English Language and Literature），並已經收到了其有條件取錄。<br />\n<br />\n拔萃女書院女狀元莊恩盈將入讀<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">英國劍橋大學人類、社會與政治科學</span></span>"},{"pid":"9433ef156ff659c464b8a4836c3e627ec5dbb9f6","tid":2120750,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:23:31.000Z","msg":"居然無醫科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60690c20560f5365a2f70fd00f8da10485e2c391","tid":2120750,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:24:12.000Z","msg":"文科社科學術科可以留意下<br />\n有d科目過咗UCAS deadline 依然有位可以報名"},{"pid":"08229ca646bd82c09deeb7ae3d160df27dbcc107","tid":2120750,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9433ef156ff659c464b8a4836c3e627ec5dbb9f6","tid":2120750,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:23:31.000Z","msg":"居然無醫科<